OL,5, A huge effort backed by the Dalai Lama 
OL,6, to save a Scottish cafe that promotes  
OL,7, Tibetan culture has succeeded after the
OL,8, #45,000 shortfall to buy it was raised.
OL,10,FReka Gawa opened the Himalaya Cafe in  
OL,11,FEdinburgh after a chance meeting with  
OL,12,Fthe spiritual leader at the Scottish   
OL,13,FParliament in 2004.                    
OL,15,FShe said he urged her to stay in       
OL,16,FScotland to promote their culture.     
OL,18,FThe landlord recently said he wanted to
OL,19,Fsell the cafe, which Reka rents, so the
OL,20,Frace was on to raise funds to buy it.  
